      "text": "This butler is a servant of the Sato family and works at their estate."
    },
    {
      "body": "When ${link_0} ${link_1} first arrived at the Sato estate, the butler escorted her to the indoor pool and announced her presence to ${link_2}, ${link_3}, and ${link_4}. To show the guest a demonstration of his pleasureful servitude, Bolin ordered him to dry off himself and ${link_5} with a towel. The butler complied, though he could not suppress his frustration when the ${link_6} immediately jumped back into the pool.",
