      "section": [
        "Butler",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "When Avatar Korra first arrived at the Sato estate, the butler escorted her to the indoor pool and announced her presence to Asami, Mako, and Bolin. To show the guest a demonstration of his pleasureful servitude, Bolin ordered him to dry off himself and Pabu with a towel. The butler complied, though he could not suppress his frustration when the earthbender immediately jumped back into the pool."
    },
    {
      "body": "When the group returned from the ${link_0}, the butler let them all back into the house and later sprayed Bolin with perfume prior to Korra's hasty exit. The next day, he was surprised by a visit from ${link_1}, ${link_2}, and the Avatar, but let them enter the estate to further question ${link_3}.",
